{"tid":810943,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"狠！中國9名檢察官 酷刑80小時逼死香港富商","createTime":"2018-09-08T11:31:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-09T07:08:18.000Z","uid":188556,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"ca9c284a850873032d3a5a12cb1835d94e3e574d","tid":810943,"uid":188556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T11:31:46.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國央視美女主播劉芳菲丈夫、香港君怡酒店老闆劉希泳，2017<br />\n年3月遭到中國羈押後，被剝奪睡眠並酷刑折磨80小時後死亡，負責審訊的中國9名檢察官<br />\n，昨（7日）因為酷刑逼供遭到起訴。<br />\n<br />\n據英國《金融時報》報導，天津市第一中級人民法院起訴書顯示，8名檢察官被指控「以<br />\n刑訊逼供」，其中2人更涉及了「故意傷害」，這項罪行最高可被判處死刑。至於第9人則<br />\n是主管審訊的檢察官，被指控「失職」。<br />\n<br />\n起訴書指出，劉希泳先是被蒙住眼睛並綁在審訊椅上，他的雙腿被高高抬起，為了加快讓<br />\n他認罪，檢察官們將劉希泳的嘴巴貼上，並用通馬桶的吸把塞住他的鼻子，再用鑰匙刺傷<br />\n他的腿。<br />\n<br />\n幾天之後，審訊檢察官多次將劉的上半身用力「折疊」到他的腿上，直到他跛足並失去知<br />\n覺。屢遭酷刑後，看守所的醫生也無法救活劉希泳。起訴書指稱，檢察官們一度陷入恐慌<br />\n，並試圖摧毀安裝在審訊室內的錄音設備。不過，對於劉希泳當時為何遭到羈押，起訴書<br />\n並未說明。<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/uvWXx2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FuvWXx2&d=Fc73ds4qqqpJJjdPsHF6JZWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=a678faa1\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/uvWXx2</a>"},{"pid":"61d5354cdf8ac83d478360e8ae0105f68207360b","tid":810943,"uid":14918,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T11:33:27.000Z","msg":"附合國情"},{"pid":"4c16384464943f370f7f72d5cac3e4fb304d1dda","tid":810943,"uid":49197,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T11:35:04.000Z","msg":"反人類罪 美國出手未"},{"pid":"d5d50fc98d0a184f711ed4cc938dff55b72ee85e","tid":810943,"uid":113626,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"4c16384464943f370f7f72d5cac3e4fb304d1dda","tid":810943,"uid":49197,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T11:35:04.000Z","msg":"反人類罪 美國出手未"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T11:42:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 亞洲係人命唔值錢區"},{"pid":"535658e2e6ec6d9133d49b88d81c8bf1d7d0a952","tid":810943,"uid":33206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T11:49:22.000Z","msg":"有罪！有罪！有罪！"},{"pid":"3a82094a6832e9403059db10b02156cbf609bbb6","tid":810943,"uid":31841,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T11:54:36.000Z","msg":"支那人黎架香港富商<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e85d0751f553b2094c8ea5161ca4bbd7a36b7a55","tid":810943,"uid":103156,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T11:57:29.000Z","msg":"Awfully inefficient. Too many man-hours consumed."},{"pid":"83a0c582eda636d31189bf7d0b78067b29f579a0","tid":810943,"uid":9286,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T11:59:51.000Z","msg":"冇提及因咩事比人拉<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 偉大的黨"},{"pid":"4d32f0edbbd8d4c32fcd2446e269fe04890e2448","tid":810943,"uid":26506,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e85d0751f553b2094c8ea5161ca4bbd7a36b7a55","tid":810943,"uid":103156,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T11:57:29.000Z","msg":"Awfully inefficient. Too many man-hours consumed."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T11:59:54.000Z","msg":"Commie bureaucratic efficiency, mate"},{"pid":"dc7974412b8ccda003f50b9ca9faa3e4ab4a6aac","tid":810943,"uid":69013,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T12:00:40.000Z","msg":"2017年都仲玩到咁顛 <br />\n港共仲叫人返大灣區住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4978c93ed825c07a8265e050d08d37e26209cadf","tid":810943,"uid":25367,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"dc7974412b8ccda003f50b9ca9faa3e4ab4a6aac","tid":810943,"uid":69013,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T12:00:40.000Z","msg":"2017年都仲玩到咁顛 <br />\n港共仲叫人返大灣區住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T12:02:07.000Z","msg":"大大聲叫人返嗰啲自己唔會返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"092292b911e57f79